{"tid":99460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浙江寧波動物園老虎咬人　中年男人「逗」虎出事","createTime":"2017-01-29T08:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T13:34:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea76cfb2f912f62cd42a537e3e911b99675e9d99","tid":99460,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170129/photo/bkncn-20170129150139346-0129_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170129151133\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170129%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170129150139346-0129_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170129151133&h=1560ff86&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一名男遊客被老虎咬住。（網上圖片） <br />\n浙江寧波雅戈爾動物園今日發生老虎咬人事件，下午約2時半，一名中年男遊客在近距離「逗」老虎時，被老虎拉入圍牆裏。職員用炮仗驅趕老虎，請遊客不要圍觀。暫時未知男遊客是否已被救出。"},{"pid":"e67de1abccd7b8680a3fd8726ab7d23e447a1131","tid":99460,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:27:35.000Z","msg":"死左"},{"pid":"429527f9addc779b05adb2e2cf1803319990b3fa","tid":99460,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:56:49.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"01046d287106a635fc7e01ed18561eeca046eef4","tid":99460,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:00:49.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"dfc1809adfa6813b149053d7b5d5c319ed8cd007","tid":99460,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:01:54.000Z","msg":"死硬啦，條友郁都冇郁"},{"pid":"97dd3a5fe408d0a8e5da15530bc7ac36de3c7aae","tid":99460,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ae3c5bcfb0808b39eb10c562cf690812e62067","tid":99460,"uid":54988,"like":0,"dislik